data.description: Exquisite water-view residence updated to the MAX! This charming single-family home in Sunrise Golf Village boasts 2 bedrooms and 2 baths, with an additional 3rd bedroom conversion in the attached 1-car garage, complete with a closet for added convenience. No HOA!  The home has been meticulously updated, featuring a new roof, and impact windows. The modern kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, perfect for entertaining guests. Generously sized driveway, allowing for multiple vehicles. The master bath has been tastefully remodeled to enhance comfort and luxury. A separate room is dedicated to the convenience of a washer and dryer. Step outside to a fenced backyard that faces the water, offering a tranquil retreat.
